OL,6,FMore than 360,000 train services
OL,7,Facross Britain were fully or part-
OL,8,Fcancelled in the past year -
OL,9,Freflecting a joint-record low in
OL,10,Freliability amid major staffing
OL,11,Fshortages.
OL,13,FSome 208,000 services were fully axed
OL,14,Fin the year to November 9, according
OL,15,Fto analysis of the latest Office of
OL,16,FRail and Road data for the PA news
OL,17,Fagency.
OL,19,FA further 161,000 were part-cancelled,
OL,20,Fmeaning they did not serve at least
OL,21,Fone of their scheduled stops.
