OL,6,FServices are being particularly badly
OL,7,Fdisrupted on Sundays as many operators
OL,8,Frely on train drivers or guards
OL,9,Fvolunteering to work paid overtime on
OL,10,Fthat day.
OL,12,FGreat Western Railway, Northern and
OL,13,FScotRail are among the operators
OL,14,Faffected.
OL,16,FMichael Solomon Williams, of pressure
OL,17,Fgroup Campaign for Better Transport,
OL,18,Fsaid delays and cancellations "erode
OL,19,Fpassengers' faith in the railways".
