OL,6,FA Department for Transport (DfT)
OL,7,Fspokesperson said: "Passengers are
OL,8,Fbeing let down by poor services, which
OL,9,Fis why we are committed to delivering
OL,10,Fthe biggest overhaul of the railways
OL,11,Fin a generation.
OL,13,F"Bringing services back into public
OL,14,Fownership will put passengers at the
OL,15,Fheart of everything we do and allow us
OL,16,Fto reinvest into our railways.
OL,18,F"We have been clear we will not
OL,19,Ftolerate poor performance and will
OL,20,Fcontinue to hold all operators to
OL,21,Faccount, regardless of ownership."
